get_OntologyNode

Source: R/queries.R
get_OntologyNode.Rd

get_OntologyNode

get_OntologyNode(
  compendium = "vespucci",
  normalization = "tpm",
  originalId = "PO_0009005",
  ontology_Name = "Plant ontology"
)

Arguments

compendium

A string - the selected compendium
normalization

A string ('legacy' as default)
originalId

A string - the ontology term
ontology_Name

A string - the name of the selected ontology

Value

A data.frame

Examples

get_OntologyNode(normalization="tpm",originalId="PO_0009005",ontology_Name="Plant ontology")
